<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku merasa kasihan padanya,
sebab itu menyelamatkan dia.</i></font>

11
00:00:57,560 --> 00:01:00,000
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku mengubah nasib Song Ma Rin.</i></font>

12
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:02,180
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tapi, setelah itu...</i></font>

13
00:01:04,330 --> 00:01:05,520
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa-apaan ini?</i></font>

14
