23
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:31,510
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jadi, aku...</i></font>

24
00:01:31,510 --> 00:01:33,660
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku lebih senang jika kita tidak saling menghubungi,</i></font>

25
00:01:34,770 --> 00:01:36,800
<font color=#FFFF00><i>atau bertemu lagi.</i></font>

26
00:01:37,170 --> 00:01:40,120
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Mari kita akhiri di sini.</i></font>

27
