35
00:02:07,170 --> 00:02:09,860
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hei, Yoo So Joon. Yoo So Joon!</i></font>

36
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:10,970
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau...</i></font>

37
00:02:12,100 --> 00:02:16,040
