52
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:58,660
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau pergilah.</i></font>

53
00:03:01,580 --> 00:03:04,110
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sebaiknya aku tidak pergi?</i></font>

54
00:03:08,770 --> 00:03:10,480
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa sekarang kita berkencan?</i></font>

55
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:19,020
