58
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:29,060
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Agar aku dapat melindungimu.</i></font>

59
00:03:29,740 --> 00:03:33,720
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Percayakan masa depanmu di tanganku.</i></font>

60
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:40,410
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Seperti itulah,
