111
00:08:14,740 --> 00:08:18,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, ini bisa jadi masalah.</font>

112
00:08:18,530 --> 00:08:21,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Gadis naif memang rumit.</font>

113
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:26,130
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aigoo... </i>aku hanya bercanda.</font>

114
00:08:26,130 --> 00:08:29,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini lezat, kok.
