115
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:32,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang berpura-pura naif?</font>

116
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan. Tidak cocok buatmu.</font>

117
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Lupakan. Aku mengerti perasaanmu.</font>

118
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:39,580
